#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:106
msgid "Edit a Plastic mesh"
msgstr "Edición de una malla"

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:107
msgid ""
"The mesh created using the **Create Mesh** button can be edited in several "
"ways. It's possible to: Move a mesh point, Swap, Collapse, Split and Cut the "
"mesh by its edges."
msgstr ""
"La malla creada mediante el botón **Crear malla* podrá ser editada de varias "
"maneras. Será posible Mover los puntos de la malla, así como Rotar, Colapsar o "
"Dividir sus bordes."

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:109
msgid "|edit_mesh_mode|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:111
msgid ""
"**Swap** an edge if you want to change the shape of a mesh triangle; "
"**Collapse** an edge if you want to join the ends of the edge; **Split** an "
"edge if you want to increase the density of the mesh at any given point; "
"**Cut** the mesh if you want to duplicate an edge to have the possibility, for "
"example, to create a hole in the mesh and be able to animate it."
msgstr ""
"**Rotar** un borde si se desea cambiar la forma de uno de los triángulos de la "
"malla; **Colapsar** un borde si se desea unir los extremos del mismo; "
"**Dividir** un borde si se desea incrementar la densidad de una malla en un "
"punto específico; **Cortar** la malla si se desea duplicar un borde para tener "
"la posibilidad de, por ejemplo, crear un hueco en la malla para poder animarlo."

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:113
msgid "The **Cut Mesh** command is visible only if the selected edges can be cut."
msgstr ""
"El comando **Cortar malla** será visible sólo cuando existiera la posibilidad "
"de cortar los bordes seleccionados."

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:115
msgid "**To enter Plastic mesh editing mode:**"
msgstr "**Para ingresar al modo de edición de mallas:**"

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:117
msgid "Select the mesh column/layer you want to modify."
msgstr "Seleccionar la columna/capa de la malla que se desee editar."

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:119
#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:179
msgid "If not already active, choose the **Plastic** tool (|plastic|)"
msgstr ""
"Si no se encontrara activa, elegir la herramienta **Plástico** (|plastic|)."

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:121
msgid "In the Tool Options bar set the **Mode:** to **Edit Mesh**."
msgstr ""
"En la barra de opciones de la herramienta definir el **Modo:** en **Editar "
"malla*."

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:123
msgid "**To move selected mesh points:**"
msgstr "**Para mover puntos seleccionados de una malla:**"

#: ../../source/create_animations_using_plastic_tool.rst:125
